\f0\b\fs42 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 4. Compiling Your Master Audio Loop\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\b0\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 To make sure your audio matches your code perfectly, compile your individual song files into one single audio file using this quick FFmpeg command in your terminal before launching the stream:\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading40\partightenfactor0

\f4\fs28\fsmilli14118 \AppleTypeServices \cf0 ffmpeg -i "concat:track1.mp3|track2.mp3|track3.mp3|track4.mp3|track5.mp3" -acodec copy lofi_music.mp3\
\pard\pardeftab560\slleading80\partightenfactor0

\f1\fs32 \AppleTypeServices\AppleTypeServicesF2293774 \cf0 This guarantees your final master 
